{"tid":411532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃耀明團結爭取公義","createTime":"2017-09-24T01:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T05:46:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d749e4affdd8301d43ad332897acbb95824a75","tid":411532,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:47:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20162146&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20162146%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170924&d=hUUeBhi%2FZbZ2J%2Bxlb%2FwNlzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e12985fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20162146%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170924&h=0e56b222\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20162146&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170924</a><br />\n<br />\n黃耀明團結爭取公義<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170924/large/24ec2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170924%2Flarge%2F24ec2p4.jpg&h=b3c04de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃耀明慨嘆言論自由越來越收窄。<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明前晚以嘉賓身份在油麻地出席「第7屆人權紀錄片電影節」開幕禮。每人都可以在手上紙牌寫上心聲，明哥的牌寫有「言論及表達自由奮鬥」。<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明在台上表示，大家都知道言論同表達空間越收越窄，希望可以為這件事奮鬥，他說：「今次最想睇《愛本是冇罪》，係關於性少眾，另一部係《唔畀我唱歌我同你死過》。呢個星期日會出席另一個演唱會，都係講言論自由，會有周博賢同何韻詩。」談到黃之鋒等一班後生仔要坐監，現場有人呼籲一人一信，明哥自言寫字麻麻，之前周博賢寫了首《後備》給他們，明哥希望大定一齊為公義努力。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：王連連<br />\n攝影：陳俊強"},{"pid":"211785104f1ed1bd7dab19226bcbe13987dd8cdd","tid":411532,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20162146&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20162146%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170924&d=hUUeBhi%2FZbZ2J%2Bxlb%2FwNlzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e12985fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20162146%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170924&h=0e56b222\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20162146&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170924</a><br />\n<br />\n黃耀明團結爭取公義<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170924/large/24ec2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170924%2Flarge%2F24ec2p4.jpg&h=b3c04de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃耀明慨嘆言論自由越來越收窄。<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明前晚以嘉賓身份在油麻地出席「第7屆人權紀錄片電影節」開幕禮。每人都可以在手上紙牌寫上心聲，明哥的牌寫有「言論及表達自由奮鬥」。<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明在台上表示，大家都知道言論同表達空間越收越窄，希望可以為這件事奮鬥，他說：「今次最想睇《愛本是冇罪》，係關於性少眾，另一部係《唔畀我唱歌我同你死過》。呢個星期日會出席另一個演唱會，都係講言論自由，會有周博賢同何韻詩。」談到黃之鋒等一班後生仔要坐監，現場有人呼籲一人一信，明哥自言寫字麻麻，之前周博賢寫了首《後備》給他們，明哥希望大定一齊為公義努力。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：王連連<br />\n攝影：陳俊強</blockquote>"},{"pid":"60f50b5f84e80ab90fe112fd4b3c8ad3d61b7713","tid":411532,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:49:01.000Z","msg":"15:00 9月24日 星期日 「共同體」－924政治犯聲援音樂集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/410519/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/410519/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8be10256804938c147f31c0ce33589c518c0e4c0","tid":411532,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15:00 9月24日 星期日 「共同體」－924政治犯聲援音樂集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/410519/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/410519/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG